5%25A8%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E7%25A8%258B&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=7853bbaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkdc/?lang=zh%E8%87%AA%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%EF%BC%8CHKDC%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E4%BF%83%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E8%AD%B0%E7%A8%8B</a>"},{"pid":"fa2cdb185fc6cf401384fbc92957bedcd9042c52","tid":2105392,"uid":295650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7db4829092860f39b2eefa1c8050825e19e2b37","tid":2105392,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056a522a3fb0738f144f3dc62732a361e3c35b9a","tid":2105392,"uid":273294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:14:08.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51de125ea7ad6e55affe9dbe3f575ac3b57fdb1c","tid":2105392,"uid":79893,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"多謝幫手嘅義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f21c2dfd85056c0a3e99db0e0f3785bf44da1c6","tid":2105392,"uid":167142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a48c689fe8658804c035b80bacbb88e0c4c2aae","tid":2105392,"uid":226955,"like":152,"dislike":0,"score":152,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:15:33.000Z","msg":"有人話，唔認同初選，所以唔投。<br />\n<br />\n有人話，冇合適選擇，所以唔投。<br />\n<br />\n有人話，預咗政府DQ，所以唔投。<br />\n<br />\n唔投票有一百個理由，最後結論是，「選舉」沒有用。<br />\n<br />\n其實今時今日，有邊一種抗爭是「有用」？作用有幾大？重要咩？<br />\n<br />\n最重要是，今日尚有一個機會凝聚人心，聚首一堂。投票數字讓同路人知道，「你未放棄呀？我都未放棄呀！」<br />\n<br />\n已經足夠。<br />\n<br />\n對呀！問題喺個制度，制度不公，選舉不公，但這不是今日才知道的事。我們不鑽孔去玩，就是被人在制度裡不斷愚弄，最後連僅餘的反對聲音也沒有。這就是「唔投票」的人想見到的願景嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果你不認同議會抗爭，你也看到同路人在「掙扎」。見到街上有人「掙扎」，身為一個人，不是上前伸出援手嗎？何況投票只是舉手之勞。<br />\n<br />\n35+有沒有用？你知我知。在極權下，有甚麼戰線是有用？<br />\n<br />\n何況對家根本沒當35+是一回事，因為選舉機器已經計過數，這是不可能任務。<br />\n<br />\n可以左右大局的，突破變數的，不是我這一種會投票的人，而是一直沒有投票的人。<br />\n<br />\n歷史會證明一切有沒有用。我只是知道，甚麼也不做，連寫入歷史的門檻也沒有。<br />\n<br />\n(圖：Stand News 立場新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTDZFeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTDZFeO.jpg&h=e3bc26ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a01ecc8bdb11717fe8d23666172c6baa6cbdf63","tid":2105392,"uid":256142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306a1bb14fc87681db4fdbbc5e0285130c98133e","tid":2105392,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26660c854b4da1598e25b0a33cbba19d07b47162","tid":2105392,"uid":61615,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:16:38.000Z","msg":"去支持返借出場地做票站嘅黃店！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /