kdc%2F%3Flang%3Dzh%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BE%2586%25EF%25BC%258CHKDC%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E7%25A8%258B&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=7853bbaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkdc/?lang=zh%E8%87%AA%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%EF%BC%8CHKDC%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E4%BF%83%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E8%AD%B0%E7%A8%8B</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">課金<br />\n課金<br />\n課金</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c742a3420a65effb6512246e50ef319f959203","tid":2105392,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51de125ea7ad6e55affe9dbe3f575ac3b57fdb1c","tid":2105392,"uid":79893,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"多謝幫手嘅義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc6c145227d401c04b476087a17f3203272c866","tid":2105392,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a48c689fe8658804c035b80bacbb88e0c4c2aae","tid":2105392,"uid":226955,"like":152,"dislike":0,"score":152,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:15:33.000Z","msg":"有人話，唔認同初選，所以唔投。<br />\n<br />\n有人話，冇合適選擇，所以唔投。<br />\n<br />\n有人話，預咗政府DQ，所以唔投。<br />\n<br />\n唔投票有一百個理由，最後結論是，「選舉」沒有用。<br />\n<br />\n其實今時今日，有邊一種抗爭是「有用」？作用有幾大？重要咩？<br />\n<br />\n最重要是，今日尚有一個機會凝聚人心，聚首一堂。投票數字讓同路人知道，「你未放棄呀？我都未放棄呀！」<br />\n<br />\n已經足夠。<br />\n<br />\n對呀！問題喺個制度，制度不公，選舉不公，但這不是今日才知道的事。我們不鑽孔去玩，就是被人在制度裡不斷愚弄，最後連僅餘的反對聲音也沒有。這就是「唔投票」的人想見到的願景嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果你不認同議會抗爭，你也看到同路人在「掙扎」。見到街上有人「掙扎」，身為一個人，不是上前伸出援手嗎？何況投票只是舉手之勞。<br />\n<br />\n35+有沒有用？你知我知。在極權下，有甚麼戰線是有用？<br />\n<br />\n何況對家根本沒當35+是一回事，因為選舉機器已經計過數，這是不可能任務。<br />\n<br />\n可以左右大局的，突破變數的，不是我這一種會投票的人，而是一直沒有投票的人。<br />\n<br />\n歷史會證明一切有沒有用。我只是知道，甚麼也不做，連寫入歷史的門檻也沒有。<br />\n<br />\n(圖：Stand News 立場新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTDZFeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTDZFeO.jpg&h=e3bc26ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c813940039a56d4f271a2f6ce5e96644b1205f","tid":2105392,"uid":302831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e958784bbd78fbb19d9955b1e44ba75bef6d9ec5","tid":2105392,"uid":23993,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ec5c09675c92cc85ecf3a87780c13eafd1bf52a3","tid":2105392,"uid":58351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:17:29.000Z","msg":"五毛: 唔夠七十萬，唔計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:29:53.000Z","msg":"個人都覺得可以再多啲<br />\n但票站少咁多兼排長龍都有上年區選民主派得票3分1以上其實真係合格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:03:56.000Z","msg":"好多人覺得反正都係投民主派<br />\n冇乜特別所謂<br />\n唔想因為自己嘅15 16影響選情"},{"pid":"3bb84062ee332e29b973ac8899500fdb2ce5b7e0","tid":2105392,"uid":172345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e958784bbd78fbb19d9955b1e44ba75bef6d9ec5","tid":2105392,"uid":23993,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ec5c09675c92cc85ecf3a87780c